Class PlatformLocalization

  • java.lang.Object
    • sketch.compiler.main.PlatformLocalization

  • public class PlatformLocalization
extends java.lang.Object
    get any variables related to this specific compile, e.g. version number, and resolve the path to the cegis binary.
